    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏本身经过专业指导，但是游戏体验因人而异，实际会存在偏差，大家如果有任何反馈欢迎留言。<br></li><li>游戏作者自身有过抑郁倾向，剧情是参考自身经历的创作，并不代表所有抑郁症人群。游戏中很多内容也是作为一种象征或寄托，抑郁症的烦恼不只有游戏里的这些，治疗抑郁症的途径也并不只有游戏中那一种。我们的目标是能让更多人感受与理解抑郁症，如有不妥之处还请大家理解。</li></ul>欢迎玩家们进入到Q群333062761进行交流反馈。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/26c938ea3e0539b643ea4576bba5fcc2.poster.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/26c938ea3e0539b643ea4576bba5fcc2.webm?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/26c938ea3e0539b643ea4576bba5fcc2.mp4?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>你身边有抑郁患者吗? 你真的了解抑郁吗？</strong>本游戏能让大家进入抑郁患者的世界，了解抑郁患者的感受。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/5ad651cfb89cac9cd7fb94351dd2aa54.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br><strong>《抑郁的房间》 是一款叙事冒险游戏</strong>，着重以氛围和体验表达抑郁的感受。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/91e8b8732d958503beb90976952a8015.poster.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/91e8b8732d958503beb90976952a8015.webm?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>玩家将体验 Moon 的日常生活，她的遭遇可能跟路人一样普通不过，</strong>但她的世界却跟其他人很不一样。因为她患上了抑郁症，生活大小事也会对她造成不同影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/5078f529d38b01028837a70773f84d99.poster.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/5078f529d38b01028837a70773f84d99.webm?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>抑郁是十分普遍的全球心理疾病，在发达城市尤为严重。</strong>本作品的使命不单是要解释抑郁，更重要的是透过游戏体验让玩家亲自感受抑郁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/59c92716b5defec8322f4f347918dc15.poster.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/59c92716b5defec8322f4f347918dc15.webm?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>我们将会把游戏一部分收入捐给慈善募捐项目，<br><strong>欢迎你加入到我们的行列。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/2cfb463534045f2bbe0a9616f387c043.poster.avif?t=1738556474\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/2cfb463534045f2bbe0a9616f387c043.webm?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056340/extras/2cfb463534045f2bbe0a9616f387c043.mp4?t=1738556474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
